            <div class="content-container">
               <h5>Placement Preparation Platform?</h5>
               <p>
                  A Placement Preparation Platform is an online platform or website that provides resources and tools to help students and job seekers prepare for placement exams and interviews. These platforms are designed to assist candidates in acquiring the necessary skills and knowledge required to succeed in various recruitment processes, such as aptitude tests, technical interviews, and group discussions.
               </p>
               <p>
                  Placement Preparation Platforms offer a variety of resources such as practice tests, mock interviews, coding challenges, study materials, and video tutorials to help students and job seekers improve their skills and knowledge. These platforms also provide insights into the recruitment process and help candidates understand the expectations of the recruiters.
               </p>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="columns image" style="background-image:url('img/2.jpg')">
