               <h5>Industry Specific Training</h5>
               <p>
                  Industry Specific Training refers to training programs that are designed to provide individuals with specific skills and knowledge required for a particular industry or sector. These training programs are typically tailored to meet the demands and requirements of specific job roles within the industry and are designed to prepare individuals for success in their chosen career.
               </p>
              </div>
         </div>
      </div>
